{"_path":"/post/20260703-ai-code-review-vibe-coded-project","_dir":"post","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"讓 AI 全面 review 我 vibe code 出來的 production 專案：20 個問題，其實只有兩種病","description":"我有一個 side project：一個台股行情資料的爬蟲系統，每天開盤自動啟動、收盤停止、晚上全量重抓，跑在雲端、透過 Telegram 推播訊號。它是我一路 vibe coding 迭代出來的——功能一直長，但我從來沒有系統性地檢視過整個 codebase。它能跑，而且跑了好幾個月。","tags":"ai, code-review, vibe-coding, nodejs, typescript, 後端開發, 技術筆記","createdByAI":true,"customCreatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:00.000Z","readingTime":{"text":"9 min read","minutes":8.12,"time":487200,"words":1624},"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我有一個 side project：一個台股行情資料的爬蟲系統，每天開盤自動啟動、收盤停止、晚上全量重抓，跑在雲端、透過 Telegram 推播訊號。它是我一路 vibe coding 迭代出來的——功能一直長，但我從來沒有系統性地檢視過整個 codebase。它能跑，而且跑了好幾個月。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"某天我讓 AI 對整個專案做一次全面 code review（針對實際的部署與排程流程，而不是抽象的 code style）。結果找到 20 個問題，從「會停機」到「會給出錯誤交易訊號」都有。但真正有價值的收穫不是那 20 條清單，而是把它們排開之後發現："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"幾乎全部可以歸成兩種病"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"病一fire-and-forget-沒有兜底"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"病一：fire-and-forget 沒有兜底"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第一類問題的共同形狀是：發起一個非同步操作，然後不管它的死活。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最典型的展品是爬蟲的生命週期。啟動端點長這樣："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{"className":"language-ts shiki shiki-themes one-dark-pro","code":"app.post('/api/start', async (c) => {\n  startCrawler(mode) // 沒有 await，也沒有 .catch\n  return c.json({ message: 'Crawler started' })\n})\n","language":"ts","meta":"","style":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":1},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"style":"--shiki-def