 date === getTodayDate()"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，讓它由資料本身決定。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"展品三：假日表只有今年。"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 判斷是否休市靠一張手工維護的假日表，裡面只有今年的日期。明年元旦起，所有假日都會被當成交易日：爬蟲照常啟動、抓到前一個交易日的殘留資料、寫進一個不存在的交易日。資料庫裡憑空多出「幽靈交易日」，而以歷史資料為基準的訊號統計全部被污染。修法是 fail fast：查表查不到該年度就直接 throw，讓系統大聲死掉，而不是安靜地做錯事。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"展品四：WebSocket 連線洩漏。"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 清理函式只在連線狀態是 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OPEN"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 時呼叫 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"close()"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。但 timeout 發生時連線往往還在 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CONNECTING"}]},{"type":"text","value":"——這時 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"close()"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 沒有效果，連線在背景完成握手後就成了沒有任何引用的活連線。修法：一律 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"terminate()"}]},{"type":"text","value":"（強制斷線），並在 close handler 裡補 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"clearTimeout"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-2","ariaDescribedBy":["footnote-label"],"dataFootnoteRef":"","id":"user-content-fnref-2"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"兩種病的共同根源"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"兩種病的共同根源"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"回頭看，這兩類病能在一個「天天正常運作」的系統裡存活這麼久，原因是一樣的："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"它們都只在特定條件下發作"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。fire-and-forget 的洞要等依賴出包才爆；靜默失效要等資料走到邊界情況（低基期、跨年度、歷史重放）才現形。日常使用給你的「它能跑」的信心，對這兩類問題完全沒有檢驗力。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這也解釋了為什麼 AI review 抓得到它們：這些問題不需要執行程式，"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"從 code 的結構就能推理出來"}]},{"type":"text","value":"——「這個 async 呼叫的錯誤會流去哪？」「這個表只有 2026 年，2027 年會發生什麼？」是純粹的紙上推演。20 個問題裡沒有任何一個需要「跑跑看才知道」。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"對-vibe-coding-的誠實結論"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"對 vibe coding 的誠實結論"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這次 review 之後我對 vibe coding 的看法是："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"它積累的債務不是 code 品質，是你不知道哪裡會壞"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。一路 vibe 出來的系統可以結構清楚、命名合理、甚至模式一致（AI 寫的 code 通常如此），但「所有失敗路徑都有人接」這件事不會自然發生——因為你每次對話的注意力都在讓功能動起來，而失敗路徑在 demo 裡永遠不會被走到。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"定期讓 AI 用「找出所有會壞的方式」的立場重讀整個專案，是我目前找到最划算的還債方式。這次 review 的 20 個問題，修復加驗證大約花了一個週末。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"後日談：修完這 20 個問題的兩週後，這個系統還是在盤中死掉了——凍結整整 12 小時，怎麼按停止都沒反應。那次事故教的東西，是任何 code review 都抓不到的另一份清單，我寫在下一篇：〈timeout 不等於 abort：一個資料庫 black-hole 殺死我爬蟲三次的覆盤〉。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"環境資訊"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"環境資訊"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Node.js: v22.x"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TypeScript: 5.x"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Runtime: Fly.io + 外部 cron 排程服務"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本文撰寫時間：2026 年 7 月，技術版本可能隨時間更新，請以官方文件為準。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"section","props":{"className":["footnotes"],"dataFootnotes":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"className":["sr-only"],"id":"footnote-label"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Reference"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{"id":"user-content-fn-1"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://nodejs.org/api/process.html#event-unhandledrejection","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Process | Node.js Documentation — Event: 'unhandledRejection'"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 未處理的 promise rejection 自 Node.js 15 起預設行為是終止 process。 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fnref-1","ariaLabel":"Back to reference 1","className":["data-footnote-backref"],"dataFootnoteBackref":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"↩"}]},{"type":"text","value":" "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fnref-1-2","ariaLabel":"Back to reference 1-2","className":["data-footnote-backref"],"dataFootnoteBackref":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"↩"},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{"id":"user-content-fn-2"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/websockets/ws/blob/master/doc/ws.md#websocketterminate","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ws - WebSocket client documentation"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"terminate()"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 立即強制斷線，與 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"close()"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 的優雅關閉握手不同，是清理 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CONNECTING"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 狀態連線的正確手段。 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fnref-2","ariaLabel":"Back to reference 2","className":["data-footnote-backref"],"dataFootnoteBackref":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"↩"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"style","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"病一fire-and-forget-沒有兜底","depth":2,"text":"病一：fire-and-forget 沒有兜底"},{"id":"病二靜默失效","depth":2,"text":"病二：靜默失效"},{"id":"兩種病的共同根源","depth":2,"text":"兩種病的共同根源"},{"id":"對-vibe-coding-的誠實結論","depth":2,"text":"對 vibe coding 的誠實結論"},{"id":"環境資訊","depth":2,"text":"環境資訊"},{"id":"footnote-label","depth":2,"text":"Reference"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:post:20260703-ai-code-review-vibe-coded-project.md","_source":"content","_file":"post/20260703-ai-code-review-vibe-coded-project.md","_stem":"post/20260703-ai-code-review-vibe-coded-project","_extension":"md","createdAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:52.000Z","updatedAt":"2026-07-03T09:44:39.000Z"}